name: Transaction Deadline
query: Select dd.tanggal as "Tanggal:Date:200",dd.note as "Note:Data:200",dd.parent as "Transaction:Link/Data Transaksi:200" , dt.alamat as "Alamat:Data:300", dt.kota as "Kota:Data:200" , dt.harga_jadi as "Harga Jadi:Currency:200" from `tabTransaction Deadline Details` dd join `tabData Transaksi` dt on dd.parent=dt.name where dd.tanggal>NOW() order by dd.tanggal
